Firstly, open the terminal, enter into the current directory

Secondly, run the StringReverseServer in terminal by input the below command line:
java -cp ServerClient.jar StringReverseServer

Thirdly, open another terminal, and run the Client in the new terminal by input the below command line:
java -cp ServerClient.jar Client

You can see "Please input a string in maximum 80 characters" in the console, so input the string, for example: hi there, I am Qing Peng.
Then the server will return the transformed string.